member.name: IEnumPublishedApps.Next
member.summary: Gets the next object in the enumeration.
member.param: A pointer to an interface reference variable that returns the next application object. Note that the category of the application object returned must match that passed into .
member.returns: Returns S_OK if an item is returned, S_FALSE if there are no more items to enumerate, a COM-defined error value otherwise.

member.name: IEnumPublishedApps.Reset
member.summary: Resets the enumeration of objects to the first item.

member.name: IEnumPublishedApps
member.summary: Exposes methods that enumerate published applications to Add/Remove Programs in the Control Panel. The object exposing this interface is requested through .
